body:
**Description**

PaintSurface event fires with old size after window maximizing/restoring.
On version 1.60 this event fires twice: with the old and new size. But after upgrade to 1.68.X only onсe, with old size only.

**Code**

Xamarin Forms app for UWP

```
using SkiaSharp.Views.Forms;
using Xamarin.Forms;

namespace App3
{
    public class MainPage : ContentPage
    {
        public MainPage()
        {
            var SKGLView = new SKGLView();
            SKGLView.PaintSurface += SKGLView_PaintSurface;
            Content = SKGLView;
        }

        private void SKGLView_PaintSurface(object sender, SKPaintGLSurfaceEventArgs e)
        {
        }
    }
}
```

**Expected Behavior**

Event fires twice with the old and new size. Or onсe with the new size.

**Actual Behavior**

Event fires with the old size.

**Basic Information**

- Version with issue:  v1.68.X
- Last known good version:  v.1.60.X
- IDE:  Visual Studio
- Platform Target Frameworks:
  - UWP:  16299
